1
00:00:12,159 --> 00:00:17,479
A wind that only seems gentle.

2
00:00:17,959 --> 00:00:22,440
Your gaze shimmers with a dark undertow.

3
00:00:23,479 --> 00:00:28,119
Who is laughing at my madness

4
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:33,560
yet indulges my startled heart.

5
00:00:34,759 --> 00:00:38,959
I see through your mask

6
00:00:39,959 --> 00:00:44,159
and let you probe my limits.

7
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:47,758
It is I who indulge.

8
00:00:47,759 --> 00:00:51,400
Love blazes like fire

9
00:00:52,799 --> 00:00:55,839
spreading.

10
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:58,879
Hard to say who crossed the line first

11
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:01,758
and who is waiting for whom to yield.

12
00:01:01,759 --> 00:01:04,598
Sharing rouge-scented smoke

13
00:01:04,599 --> 00:01:07,638
and the flame that collides at our lips

14
00:01:07,639 --> 00:01:10,000
fiercer than any tender lingering

15
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:12,838
a duel that stakes our pride

16
00:01:12,839 --> 00:01:18,080
whether a calamity decreed by fate

17
00:01:18,279 --> 00:01:23,319
or sweetness bestowed by heaven

18
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:27,638
I still choose craving, wrath, and folly's

19
00:01:27,639 --> 00:01:30,278
mad notion

20
00:01:30,279 --> 00:01:33,400
made real.

21
00:01:34,639 --> 00:01:40,719
To hold your gaze is far too perilous

22
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:46,838
I walk devoutly toward my ruin.

23
00:01:46,839 --> 00:01:54,839
You are my abyss.

24
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:03,918
You are my

25
00:02:03,919 --> 00:02:08,479
sunshine.

26
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:16,000
"To My Shore"

27
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:23,119
Rarely does a gift affect
me right to my core.

28
00:02:25,399 --> 00:02:27,719
I've got a meeting in half an hour,

29
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:30,720
so I can give you ten minutes before that.

30
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,160
I brought Lu Zhen to
apologize to you, Ms. Shi.

31
00:02:33,559 --> 00:02:34,919
Apologize for what?

32
00:02:35,559 --> 00:02:38,160
Men and women—love is about chemistry.

33
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,279
If Little Lu isn't into me,

34
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,279
I can't force it.

35
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,720
Honestly,

36
00:02:45,679 --> 00:02:46,879
at my age,

37
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,838
if I try hard enough I could
probably give birth to him.

38
00:02:48,839 --> 00:02:49,839
Lu Zhen,

39
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,759
What are you waiting
for? Apologize to Ms. Shi.

40
00:02:52,679 --> 00:02:53,799
Ms. Shi, I'm sorry.

41
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,800
I was wrong.

42
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,399
I have let you down egregiously.

43
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,639
I didn't know better.

44
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,999
I didn't understand the situation,

45
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,520
I...
Lu Zhen,

46
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,440
If you're apologizing, show some sincerity.

47
00:03:02,559 --> 00:03:04,880
Is Ms. Shi's time just for
you to waste by rambling?

48
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,919
Ms. Shi, I was wrong.

49
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,856
I accepted the date without
understanding the situation.

50
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,240
Please forgive me.

51
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,558
Why does everyone make
me out to be the villain?

52
00:03:21,559 --> 00:03:23,758
If I were you that day,

53
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,959
I wouldn't have let Lu Zhen

54
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,600
walk out of that club in one piece.

55
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,895
And I wouldn't have
waited around all day today,

56
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:30,880
carving time out of a
packed schedule to see him.

57
00:03:31,399 --> 00:03:34,039
So “villain” doesn't suit you at all.

58
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:39,559
Lu Zhen,

59
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:40,919
Who told you to get up?

60
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,720
What...

61
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,639
did they assign Little Lu a new agent?

62
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,360
Ms. Shi,

63
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,278
I'm Lu Zhen's ex...

64
00:03:53,279 --> 00:03:54,279
You Shulang.

65
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,639
Ex what?

66
00:03:56,399 --> 00:03:57,399
Boyfriend?

67
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:02,359
So the agency recommended a gay guy to me?

68
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,360
Please don't be upset

69
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,375
it has nothing to do with the company;

70
00:04:05,399 --> 00:04:06,639
this was all Lu Zhen's fault.

71
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,399
He wanted the endorsement

72
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,039
and wanted to build connections,

73
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,800
but he didn't communicate
clearly with the agency.

74
00:04:13,119 --> 00:04:15,080
He accepted your request while in a daze,

75
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,800
but he knew he shouldn't pretend
to be straight and deceive anyone.

76
00:04:18,559 --> 00:04:19,880
He chickened out that night.

77
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,239
The company was furious...

78
00:04:21,799 --> 00:04:23,119
and wanted to teach him a lesson.

79
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:27,160
That wound on your
forehead—someone hit you?

80
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,920
I had it coming.

81
00:04:31,359 --> 00:04:33,359
At least you've got a conscience.

82
00:04:34,119 --> 00:04:37,599
Better than the ones who pop pills and still
pretend to be straight to get the job done.

83
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,839
So, Little Lu was your…

84
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:42,799
ex-boyfriend?

85
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,959
Yes.

86
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,959
And you still step up
when your ex is in trouble?

87
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,760
This is the last time I'm doing this.

88
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,799
I'm paying him back for what we had,

89
00:04:54,239 --> 00:04:55,239
and after today,

90
00:04:56,559 --> 00:04:58,279
I'm done.

91
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,480
Why did you break up?

92
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,640
He's such a good boyfriend.

93
00:05:41,239 --> 00:05:43,119
Guess you weren't satisfied.

94
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,079
Some men

95
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,559
can't share hardship;

96
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,519
some can't share riches.

97
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,760
If I'd met a decent man,

98
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:56,080
I wouldn't be booking pretty little boys
every night to pass the time.

99
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,720
Lu Zhen is young.

100
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:01,200
He idealizes everything...

101
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,479
love, work.

102
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,720
He stumbled this time,

103
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,800
and I hope that he'll
definitely learn from it.

104
00:06:07,119 --> 00:06:08,119
So.

105
00:06:08,799 --> 00:06:10,600
Please, do us this kindness

106
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,399
and forgive him.

107
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,720
Not many men will lower
themselves for an ex.

108
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:22,720
I'll accept this favor from you,
Mr. You.

109
00:06:25,679 --> 00:06:27,399
I won't replace the spokesperson.

110
00:06:28,359 --> 00:06:29,359
Lu Zhen...

111
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,319
I liked you

112
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:34,679
because you reminded me
a bit of my ex-husband when he was young.

113
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:40,200
Just don't become as black-hearted
as he turned out to be.

114
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:48,640
I'm sorry—really sorry.

115
00:06:56,559 --> 00:06:58,000
What a pity, Mr. You.

116
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,239
If you liked women,

117
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,200
no matter the cost,

118
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,200
I'd make you mine.

119
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,480
You're kind

120
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,720
and beautiful,

121
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,159
You'll meet the right person.

122
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,239
The right person…

123
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,760
have you met yours?

124
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,920
Before that night,

125
00:07:28,119 --> 00:07:30,160
I thought I had.

126
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:34,500
(Episode 9)

127
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:36,839
Sawadee ka.

128
00:07:39,799 --> 00:07:40,880
This way, please.

129
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,839
There you are, Director You.

130
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,399
Second Young Master,

131
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,680
Sorry to keep you waiting,

132
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:49,279
Not at all...

133
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,160
you're ten minutes early.

134
00:07:56,239 --> 00:07:57,600
Refined taste...

135
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,238
finding a traditional
troupe like this in Bangkok.

136
00:08:00,239 --> 00:08:01,559
Just putting on airs.

137
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:03,519
I'm learning from our third brother...

138
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:08,279
sampling the sights, cuisine,
and beauties of Hua culture.

139
00:08:12,679 --> 00:08:14,399
Let's be direct.

140
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,520
What did you want to see me about?

141
00:08:18,239 --> 00:08:19,519
I heard

142
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,200
you and Fan Xiao broke up.

143
00:08:21,679 --> 00:08:22,679
Is it true?

144
00:08:23,119 --> 00:08:24,719
It seems like you have something to say.

145
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,880
If we're going to talk in circles,

146
00:08:28,119 --> 00:08:29,399
we might as well enjoy the show.

147
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:30,200
Fine...

148
00:08:30,201 --> 00:08:32,400
Then I'll lay it all out on the line.

149
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,280
After what he did to you,

150
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,000
you really don't want revenge?

151
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,760
What's funny?

152
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:43,799
So Second Young Master
has sounded the war drums...

153
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,640
and wants a blade to wield.

154
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,359
We each get what we need.

155
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,479
Don't say I'm using you as a blade.

156
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,320
And in your view,

157
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,000
how should I take revenge?

158
00:08:57,599 --> 00:09:00,319
There are a million ways.

159
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:03,319
I've found you the
simplest, quickest path...

160
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,359
to vent your anger

161
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,880
and make some money.

162
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,039
To vent my anger? How?

163
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,960
I'd love to know.

164
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:15,719
Don't you want to hear
how you profit first?

165
00:09:16,599 --> 00:09:20,520
I heard you've been selling
your apartment to repay Fan Xiao.

166
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,118
No need.

167
00:09:22,119 --> 00:09:23,119
Help me with one thing...

168
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,960
Help me with one thing...

169
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,000
and everything on this cheque is yours.

170
00:09:27,719 --> 00:09:29,160
All the money in this
cheque is yours.

171
00:09:29,184 --> 00:09:30,839
It's more than enough to cover
your brother's debt

172
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,840
and then some.

173
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:36,080
You get your anger out and walk
away with cash—best of both worlds.

174
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:40,799
That much?

175
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,840
What do you need me to do?

176
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,080
Nothing hard.

177
00:09:47,359 --> 00:09:50,038
Just slip this drive

178
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:53,000
into Fan Xiao's work laptop—quietly.

179
00:09:54,359 --> 00:09:55,359
And that's all.

180
00:09:55,719 --> 00:09:56,719
And then?

181
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,599
Then we wait.

182
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,560
He's doing something illegal?

183
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,679
Director You,

184
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:08,280
If he ends up in handcuffs,

185
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,840
won't that make you feel better?

186
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,799
I watched him build the tower high;

187
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,039
I watched him feed his guests;

188
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:40,577
I watched the tower collapse.

189
00:10:40,602 --> 00:10:43,562
[TN: Quote from the classic play "The
Peach Blossom Fan" by Kong Shangren]

190
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:46,799
Second Young Master,

191
00:10:48,719 --> 00:10:50,400
there's nothing left between us.

192
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:53,239
Settle your family feud yourselves.

193
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,799
Thank you for the tea...

194
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
but

195
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,320
it's gone cold.

196
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,559
Director You,

197
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:10,359
Director You, wait. Sit.

198
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:15,559
I never took you
for a man who stands idle when insulted.

199
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,799
I've got a recording of Fan Xiao...

200
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,520
don't you want to hear

201
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:24,559
how he talked about you with others?

202
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,159
You wiretapped him?

203
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:30,678
Our third brother is
too careful and sharp...

204
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:31,880
I can't wiretap him.

205
00:11:32,119 --> 00:11:33,959
I bought the audio from the Shi family...

206
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,399
It seems like they have someone on call.

207
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,560
I thought it was interesting,

208
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:40,039
so I bought the audio they
recorded while spying on him.

209
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,079
I didn't expect what I heard.

210
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:45,239
Even I thought he went too far.

211
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,080
Director You,

212
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:48,559
Wanna hear?

213
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,039
No need.

214
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,080
Not interested.

215
00:11:57,159 --> 00:12:00,280
When life gets boring,
I used him to kill time.

216
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,200
When I've had my fill, I get rid of him.

217
00:12:04,719 --> 00:12:05,919
Since he's being ungrateful,

218
00:12:06,598 --> 00:12:07,598
then I'll coax him back,

219
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,719
then dump him hard.

220
00:12:10,479 --> 00:12:11,239
Director You,

221
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,479
You can accept that?

222
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,119
I wouldn't be able to at all.

223
00:12:14,479 --> 00:12:15,520
As far as I know,

224
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:17,559
Fan Xiao still has a thing for you.

225
00:12:17,599 --> 00:12:19,400
Why don't you pretend
to make up with him...

226
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,000
earn his trust...

227
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,520
and then

228
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,280
slip this drive

229
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:26,719
into his laptop?

230
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,558
Then it'll be mission accomplished.

231
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:29,880
You'll make money

232
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,039
and vent your anger.

233
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,679
Why not?

234
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,679
Second Young Master,

235
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,520
If you like the recording,

236
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,880
keep it.

237
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,640
You're brothers...

238
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:48,799
special hobbies aren't surprising.

239
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,159
I'm going after that pervert.

240
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:11,719
Have fun.

241
00:13:12,119 --> 00:13:15,759
For now, it looks pretty good.

242
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:16,919
You wait, You Shulang

243
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,960
I love you.

244
00:13:18,559 --> 00:13:20,918
I mean it, You Shulang.

245
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:24,039
When life gets boring,
I used him to kill time.

246
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:27,960
When I've had my fill, I get rid of him.

247
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,200
Since he's being ungrateful,

248
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,200
then I'll coax him back,

249
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,000
then dump him hard.

250
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:15,760
What's the matter?

251
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,080
Bai Ting,

252
00:14:18,119 --> 00:14:19,119
I need a favor...

253
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,880
get someone drunk for me.

254
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,759
How come I've never seen you...

255
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,639
Are you new here?

256
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:29,959
New?

257
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,520
I'm just not enough for you to see me.

258
00:14:31,719 --> 00:14:32,879
I'm hurt.

259
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:35,280
Isn't Bai Ting the sweet-and-pure type?

260
00:14:35,359 --> 00:14:36,719
Look at her outfit.

261
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:40,559
Those lashes on her
lids could rake my face.

262
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:42,256
She wants to latch onto Third Young Master.

263
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:43,760
Everyone knows

264
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:47,400
he likes 'em curvy and bold.

265
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:50,679
How can my sweetie stop feeling wronged?

266
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:53,520
Want me to buy you a bag?

267
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:56,520
How could I make you
spend money, Young Master.

268
00:14:56,599 --> 00:14:57,799
How about

269
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:00,280
three penalty shots instead?

270
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:03,079
Fine, fine.

271
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:03,840
Tonight

272
00:15:03,841 --> 00:15:05,760
I'll drink with you till you're happy.

273
00:15:06,559 --> 00:15:09,880
But before we drink, let me have a kiss...

274
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:12,960
What the—who are you?

275
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:16,679
It's you.

276
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:18,400
You're...

