it'll be quick to produce and launch.

561
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:12,280
No other pharmaceutical companies involved?

562
00:34:12,399 --> 00:34:13,360
There's some support.

563
00:34:13,399 --> 00:34:16,639
But the focus is on
developing the Changling brand.

564
00:34:17,399 --> 00:34:19,399
Once we get this project up and running,

565
00:34:19,879 --> 00:34:23,919
we'll be able to roll out other projects one by one.

566
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:27,959
For all of these popular products in Thailand,

567
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:30,799
we'll can use the Changling brand

568
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:32,479
and bring them to market.

569
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:33,879
The investors say,

570
00:34:33,919 --> 00:34:35,679
as long as marketing is done right,

571
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,879
we can easily make the brand a success.

572
00:34:39,239 --> 00:34:40,000
The investors?

573
00:34:40,001 --> 00:34:41,639
There's already funding?

574
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,639
Yeah.

575
00:34:42,640 --> 00:34:44,800
Where else would we get the money?

576
00:34:44,879 --> 00:34:47,799
And besides, we only know R&D.

577
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,360
We're not in sales.

578
00:34:50,199 --> 00:34:50,479
Hmm.
Shulang.

579
00:34:52,679 --> 00:34:54,399
You're my best student.

580
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:59,560
You were overqualified for our school from your exam scores back then.

581
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:01,560
You had such great graduate scores.

582
00:35:02,479 --> 00:35:06,280
But you rushed to work to
support your younger brother.

583
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:08,000
You couldn't continue your studies.

584
00:35:09,399 --> 00:35:13,159
And you ended up in a
job that wasn't in your field.

585
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:14,776
And in my heart of hearts,

586
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:17,000
I've never let it go.

587
00:35:17,199 --> 00:35:21,040
So, now this must be a result of our unfinished
teacher-student bond.

588
00:35:22,239 --> 00:35:23,638
I'm in Thailand.

589
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:26,199
I can't do it here without someone I trust.

590
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:28,040
Come and help your teacher.

591
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,080
Teacher.

592
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:34,359
The thing is, my job...

593
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:36,839
"Though none may lend a hand to lift my lofty dreams,"

594
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:39,800
"I shall tread through snow and reach the mountain's peak."

595
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:42,760
I know that you've relied on yourself

596
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:45,800
to make it to to where you are at Bohai.

597
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,199
And it wasn't easy.

598
00:35:47,239 --> 00:35:48,719
But really ask yourself...

599
00:35:48,959 --> 00:35:51,360
do you like this job?

600
00:35:57,959 --> 00:35:59,280
Can't say I like it.

601
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,800
Toasting and chatting.

602
00:36:00,801 --> 00:36:01,919
Welcoming and sending off.

603
00:36:02,399 --> 00:36:03,519
I've long grown tired of it.

604
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,359
But right now,

605
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:07,399
you're worried about the pay?

606
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,399
Don't be.

607
00:36:09,521 --> 00:36:11,885
Didn't I tell you we have investors?

608
00:36:11,919 --> 00:36:14,959
Come be my deputy team lead

609
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,560
and manage all the external affairs.

610
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:21,040
I'll pay you… this much.

611
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:24,280
My, you've certainly changed a lot.

612
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:26,399
Boss Huang has really become a boss!

613
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,120
Right.

614
00:36:29,159 --> 00:36:31,759
I heard you sold your apartment,

615
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:33,080
and need a place.

616
00:36:33,399 --> 00:36:36,000
The investor's covering more than money...

617
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:40,000
offices and housing are included.

618
00:36:42,034 --> 00:36:45,658
If I stay at Bohai,
I'll inevitably see Fan Xiao again.

619
00:36:46,366 --> 00:36:47,366
He's unpredictable,

620
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,918
and I've already

621
00:36:48,919 --> 00:36:50,639
been far too irrational in this relationship.

622
00:36:51,120 --> 00:36:52,478
Maybe leaving now

623
00:36:52,479 --> 00:36:53,679
is the smartest move.

624
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,000
Well?

625
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,719
You in, Shulang?

626
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,000
Sir...

627
00:37:00,399 --> 00:37:01,320
I'll follow however you plan it.
Good.

628
00:37:02,121 --> 00:37:04,399
Then it's a deal.

629
00:37:04,479 --> 00:37:06,718
The project's already started.

630
00:37:06,719 --> 00:37:08,800
I need you on-site ASAP.

631
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:09,840
So...

632
00:37:10,199 --> 00:37:13,599
hurry up and resign tomorrow and come over.

633
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:14,600
Tomorrow?

634
00:37:16,175 --> 00:37:19,399
I'll need time
to hand over my work.

635
00:37:20,479 --> 00:37:21,519
And...

636
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:24,000
who's the investor behind this team?

637
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,000
It's…

638
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:30,199
Xinruida.

639
00:37:30,959 --> 00:37:32,079
Xinruida.

640
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:35,000
Funding stuff isn't your lane.

641
00:37:35,025 --> 00:37:36,626
You definitely wouldn't know them.

642
00:37:37,120 --> 00:37:38,120
Mm.

643
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,840
All right, sir.

644
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:41,479
I'll get on it quickly.

645
00:38:12,879 --> 00:38:13,879
Sir.

646
00:38:14,679 --> 00:38:15,679
Ah, Shulang...

647
00:38:15,879 --> 00:38:16,879
have a seat.

648
00:38:18,879 --> 00:38:19,879
Sit.

649
00:38:23,919 --> 00:38:24,919
Shulang,

650
00:38:25,159 --> 00:38:28,000
thanks to you leading the cleanup,

651
00:38:28,239 --> 00:38:30,120
this room finally looks
presentable, hahaha.

652
00:38:31,560 --> 00:38:32,718
Professor Huang,

653
00:38:32,719 --> 00:38:35,280
what's the deal with the investor?

654
00:38:35,399 --> 00:38:37,080
I still know nothing.

655
00:38:38,199 --> 00:38:41,879
You just arrived; your
to-do list is a mile long.

656
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,959
Investors are just money men.

657
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:48,159
No need to study them.

658
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:50,919
Anyway, they'll be here in a minute...

659
00:38:50,959 --> 00:38:52,039
we'll talk as we meet them.

660
00:38:52,560 --> 00:38:53,560
Mm.

661
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:54,919
Mr. Huang...

662
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,238
your guests are here.

663
00:38:56,239 --> 00:38:57,239
Please.

664
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,759
In the crowd

665
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:33,320
I was spotted in an instant.

666
00:39:34,439 --> 00:39:36,839
The desolation in your eyes.

667
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:39,999
Hiding the same fire inside.

668
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:42,678
No need for words.

669
00:39:42,679 --> 00:39:46,000
No need to ask what's right or wrong.

670
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,519
The moment we drew close.

671
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:51,239
The outcome was already destined.

672
00:39:59,399 --> 00:40:01,919
Is the moth drawn to the light.

673
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:05,280
Or the whale sinking into the deep.

674
00:40:05,879 --> 00:40:07,398
With nothing but solitary courage

675
00:40:07,399 --> 00:40:09,959
I wager it all on tomorrow.

676
00:40:11,199 --> 00:40:13,958
The walls of the world.

677
00:40:13,959 --> 00:40:17,239
What does it matter if I break them down.

678
00:40:18,399 --> 00:40:20,678
My chest burns with heat.

679
00:40:20,679 --> 00:40:22,879
Screaming only for you

680
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:26,678
I'll love you until it boils over.

681
00:40:26,679 --> 00:40:28,959
Loving without a care for the world.

682
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:30,718
Like two stars.

683
00:40:30,719 --> 00:40:32,719
Colliding and shattering in the night sky.

684
00:40:32,919 --> 00:40:33,919
Even if it's just for a moment.

685
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:35,519
It's more than enough to surpass forever.

686
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,799
Hate and love both burn brightly.

687
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:39,478
Loving until the sky falls dark.

688
00:40:39,479 --> 00:40:41,439
Loving until we reach the end of the road.

689
00:40:42,199 --> 00:40:43,238
Before the altar.

690
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:45,359
We burn all the incense.

691
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,438
Not asking for the next life.

692
00:40:46,439 --> 00:40:47,958
Only desiring this moment.

693
00:40:47,959 --> 00:40:49,158
Drowning together with you in.

694
00:40:49,159 --> 00:40:51,399
This blazing fire of fate
